description.text:
Just a simple bridge for your pool table.<br />
You can attach easily (and temporarily) to the end of one of your Pool/Cue Sticks. It allows you to sink those shots that are......just......out.............of............................reach.<br />
Note that another .stl file that adds &quot;side&quot; guides is also provided and attached. &quot;Pool_Table_Bridge_2.stl&quot;
